mutt-wizard: mutt-wizard (short description of app)
mutt-wizard:
mutt-wizard: A full-featured and autoconfigured email client on the terminal
mutt-wizard: with neomutt.
mutt-wizard:   - Mail stored offline enabling the ability to:
mutt-wizard:     * view and write emails while you're away from the internet
mutt-wizard:     * make backups
mutt-wizard:   - Provides a mailsync script that can be scheduled to run as often
mutt-wizard:     as you like, which downloads/syncs mail and notifies you when new
mutt-wizard:     mail has arrived.
